      <h2>Markdown → 小红书图片</h2>
      <textarea id="md" style="flex:1; width:100%; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; font-size:14px; padding:12px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;" placeholder="在此粘贴 Markdown"># 小红书笔记制作工具

